#@ String (value = "<html><h2> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &gt;&gt;&gt; Tips</h2><br><p>Before you begin, organize a folder containing several subfolders:<ul><li>1-Raw</li><li>2-MIP</li><li>3-Mask</li><li>4-Spots</li></ul>Verify that raw images have the same suffix for each channel.<br>For example, all red channels end with <code>\"w1Cy3.tif\"</code>.<br>Otherwise, use the Lupas Rename software to simultaneously rename the images in the same folder. </p><i>Be careful, the analysis is done from images in <code>.tif</code> format.</i></html>", persist = true, visibility = MESSAGE) message
